Class ChartGraphics

  • java.lang.Object
    • starvationevasion.client.MegaMawile.ChartGraphics

  • public class ChartGraphics
extends java.lang.Object
    Class is used to create charts from statistics that have been stored. Methods in the class only need the specification and in turn a chart is returned to the gui.
